flowchart TD
    %% Entities
    Buyer([Buyer])
    Artisan([Artisan])
    System([Craftistan Backend])
    Gemini[(Google Gemini AI)]
    
    %% Core Flow
    Artisan -->|1. Creates Product| System
    System -->|2. Background Translation| Gemini
    Gemini -.->|3. Translated Content| System
    
    Buyer -->|4. Browses Catalog| System
    Buyer -->|5. Adds to Wishlist/Cart| System
    Buyer -->|6. Places Order| System
    
    System -->|7. Deducts Stock & Saves Order| System
    System -->|8. Order Notification| Artisan
    
    Artisan -->|9. Fulfills & Ships Order| System
    Buyer -->|10. Leaves Verified Review| System

    %% AI Support
    Buyer -->|Queries| Chatbot[AI Chat Assistant]
    Chatbot -->|Converses| Gemini
